name = "Golden Terraform Azure WebApp "
description = "A standardized infrastructure-as-code deployment template for Azure App Services. It automates the end-to-end provisioning of Web Apps, App Service Plans, and VNet integrations using versioned Terraform modules. The template includes built-in security gates for static analysis (tfsec/Checkov), plan-to-apply consistency checks, and state-file management. Ideal for enforcing organizational cloud guardrails, ensuring that all web infrastructure is secure by default, cost-optimized, and compliant with corporate networking standards."